\log\ell_{n}\left(Y;\mu,\sigma^{2}\right)=-\frac{n}{2}\log\gamma-\frac{n}{2}\log\pi-\frac{1}{2\gamma}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\left(Y_{i}-\mu\right)^{2}
\]

